12.short_description: E-commerce retailer selling supplements to Spanish-speaking Latin Americans

18.description:
NutriOptima is an e-commerce retailer focused on vitamins, minerals, superfoods and supplements, which gives their customers access to both their USA manufactured NutriOptima products and partner brands. We add value to the market by providing a detailed Spanish guide that covers around 300 supplements and 50 health conditions. This guide answers their clients’ key questions such as what are the health benefits, side effects and best dosage of a specific supplement, and proposes supplement-based solutions to improve certain health conditions.

Their key advantage is a simple but innovative 4-step diagnosis tool based on both a matrix linking supplements to health conditions and on correlations between supplements’ effects (underlying data coming from medical studies). This tool allows customers to quickly get access to supplements relevant to them based on their age, gender and health condition. It also tells them which supplements to avoid due to lack of proven benefits or contraindications.
